{"id":"algum","term":"Algum","source":"Easton's Bible Dictionary (M.G. Easton, 1897)","html":"<p>(<a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"2 Chronicles 2:8\">2 Chr. 2:8</a>; <a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"2 Chronicles 9:10\">9:10</a>,<a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"2 Chronicles 9:11\">11</a>), the same as almug (<a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"1 Kings 10:11\">1 Kings 10:11</a>).</p>\n\u0000","refs":["2 Chronicles 2:8","2 Chronicles 9:10","2 Chronicles 9:11","1 Kings 10:11"]}